v 0.2.0 - beta4
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Kipi-plugins NEW FEATURES:

RemoveRedEyes  : New plugin to remove red eyes in batch. Tool is based on OpenCV library.
AcquireImages  : Under Windows, TWAIN interface is used to scan image using flat scanner.
SlideShow      : Normal effects are back.
SlideShow      : New effect "Cubism".

Kipi-plugins BUG FIXING from B.K.O (http://bugs.kde.org):

001 ==> 172910 : GalleryExport      : Gallery crash (letting crash digiKam) with valid data and url.
002 ==> 161855 : GalleryExport      : Remote Gallery Sync loses password.
003 ==> 154752 : GalleryExport      : Export to Gallery2 seems to fail, but in fact works.
004 ==> 

v 0.2.0 - beta3
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Kipi-plugins NEW FEATURES:

General        : all plugins can be compiled natively under Microsoft Windows.

Kipi-plugins BUG FIXING from B.K.O (http://bugs.kde.org):

001 ==> 172283 : SlideShow          : SlideShow crashes host application 
002 ==> 172337 : SlideShow          : Slideshow enhancements by ken-burns effects.
003 ==> 173276 : SlideShow	    : digikam crashs after closing 

v 0.2.0 - beta2
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Kipi-plugins NEW FEATURES:

DNGConverter   : New plugin to convert RAW camera image to Digital NeGative (DNG)
SlideShow      : Now you can play your favourite music during slideshow.

Kipi-plugins BUG FIXING from B.K.O (http://bugs.kde.org):

001 ==> 150076 : SlideShow          : Playing music during a slideshow  

v 0.2.0 - beta1
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Kipi-plugins NEW FEATURES:

General        : Port to CMake/KDE4/QT4. 
JPEGLossLess   : XMP metadata support. 
RAWConverter   : XMP metadata support. 
TimeAdjust     : XMP metadata support. 
MetadataEdit   : XMP metadata support with EXIF, IPTC, and Comments editor to sync XMP tags.
MetadataEdit   : IPTC Editor dialog is more compliant with IPTC.org recommendations.
MetadataEdit   : IPTC Editor add the capability to set multiple values for a tag.
SendImages     : Complete re-write of emailing tool.
GPSSync        : New tool to edit GPS track list using googlemaps.
RAWConverter   : Raw files are decoded in 16 bits color depth using same auto-gamma and auto-white 
                 methods provided by dcraw with 8 bits color depth RAW image decoding. 
SlideShow      : Now filenames, captions and progress indicators can have transparent
                 backgrounds with OpenGL SlideShow as well.
SlideShow      : Added thumbnails into image list.

Kipi-plugins BUG FIXING from B.K.O (http://bugs.kde.org):

001 ==> 135451 : GPSSync            : Improve the gui of the gpssync plugin.
002 ==> 135386 : GPSSync            : Show track on the google map.
003 ==> 149497 : GPSSync            : Geolocalization kipi plugin does not work with non-jpeg file types.
004 ==> 145746 : GPSSync            : Do not recreate thumbs when geolocalizing images.
005 ==> 134299 : SimpleViewerExport : Read orientation of image from EXIF.
006 ==> 158792 : GPSsync            : Plugin do not working with Canon RAW CR2.
007 ==> 165078 : GPSSync            : GPS correlator does not show thumbnails.
008 ==> 165278 : GPSSync            : Geotagging dialog doesn't display all thumbnails.

